WEBVTT

00:00:00.199 --> 00:00:02.950
Hey, good morning family, praise the Lord.

00:00:02.960 --> 00:00:05.070
Thank you for joining us. It's Diana and

00:00:05.080 --> 00:00:07.549
Brandon again, the dynamic

00:00:07.549 --> 00:00:07.559
duo.

00:00:07.559 --> 00:00:10.350
I'm excited to be here, baby. I

00:00:10.360 --> 00:00:12.749
have some things on my heart, and I know

00:00:12.759 --> 00:00:15.509
you do. We were talking about it today

00:00:15.519 --> 00:00:18.950
and what we feel in the atmosphere.

00:00:18.960 --> 00:00:21.710
You can feel there's a tangible

00:00:21.710 --> 00:00:21.720
feeling that

00:00:21.720 --> 00:00:24.349
something is about to happen,

00:00:24.359 --> 00:00:27.390
like a puzzle you just focus on and

00:00:27.390 --> 00:00:27.400
try

00:00:27.400 --> 00:00:29.230
to figure out all the pieces,

00:00:29.240 --> 00:00:31.589
and it's too hard. So you just have to

00:00:31.599 --> 00:00:33.470
focus on the piece that you have in your

00:00:33.480 --> 00:00:35.990
hand, praying that

00:00:35.990 --> 00:00:36.000
piece

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:38.110
through instead of

00:00:38.120 --> 00:00:39.869
thinking about the whole, like, 'Well, this

00:00:39.879 --> 00:00:42.470
is overwhelming, all of this needs

00:00:42.470 --> 00:00:42.480
prayer.'You

00:00:42.480 --> 00:00:43.869
just focus

00:00:43.879 --> 00:00:46.110
on one piece at a time, the piece that's

00:00:46.120 --> 00:00:48.590
right in front of you, and you pray that

00:00:48.600 --> 00:00:50.709
through. And when that piece goes in and

00:00:50.719 --> 00:00:52.630
you see it go into the puzzle,

00:00:52.640 --> 00:00:54.189
then He'll hand you another piece and

00:00:54.199 --> 00:00:55.910
you just pray over that piece and you

00:00:55.920 --> 00:00:57.510
keep doing it until the whole picture's

00:00:57.520 --> 00:00:59.950
done. Sometimes we just get

00:00:59.960 --> 00:01:02.349
overwhelmed in prayer thinking about

00:01:02.349 --> 00:01:02.359
how

00:01:02.359 --> 00:01:05.149
this is a mess, this

00:01:05.159 --> 00:01:08.429
whole puzzle needs this,

00:01:08.429 --> 00:01:08.439
and

00:01:08.439 --> 00:01:10.550
I can't even see what it's going to be

00:01:10.560 --> 00:01:11.630
like. You don't even know what the

00:01:11.640 --> 00:01:13.350
picture is or where we are going

00:01:13.360 --> 00:01:15.429
right now. And that's where I felt

00:01:15.439 --> 00:01:17.270
like when I'm praying, I asked, 'What

00:01:17.270 --> 00:01:17.280
is

00:01:17.280 --> 00:01:19.270
priority number one, Lord, on

00:01:19.280 --> 00:01:23.030
Your heart?'Because right now the canvas

00:01:23.030 --> 00:01:23.040
she's

00:01:23.040 --> 00:01:24.310
talking about, this massive

00:01:24.320 --> 00:01:28.870
canvas, this puzzle, is overwhelming.

00:01:30.720 --> 00:01:33.469
I was praying over it, and I

00:01:33.479 --> 00:01:36.190
know that what I have right now,

00:01:36.200 --> 00:01:38.670
what I've seen in the spirit and what I

00:01:38.680 --> 00:01:42.830
saw in a video back, is another

00:01:42.830 --> 00:01:42.840
storm—a

00:01:42.840 --> 00:01:46.590
major shaking to awaken is

00:01:46.600 --> 00:01:49.190
coming, you all. After I stopped

00:01:49.200 --> 00:01:51.550
praying with you, I prayed for at least

00:01:51.560 --> 00:01:54.550
another hour,

00:01:54.560 --> 00:01:58.109
praying into that because the spirit

00:01:58.119 --> 00:02:00.789
of intercession hit me so hard. It was so

00:02:00.799 --> 00:02:03.310
heavy. I came in, sat on

00:02:03.320 --> 00:02:04.990
the couch, and

00:02:05.000 --> 00:02:06.910
I started hearing

00:02:06.920 --> 00:02:08.830
prophetically about our life. The Lord

00:02:08.840 --> 00:02:10.790
just started downloading

00:02:10.800 --> 00:02:14.430
again, warning us of what's coming. I saw

00:02:14.440 --> 00:02:17.229
a rectangular window before me in the

00:02:17.239 --> 00:02:20.470
spirit realm, and the Lord told me there

00:02:20.480 --> 00:02:23.790
is going to be a window of

00:02:23.800 --> 00:02:25.949
blessing. I'm telling you, you can see it

00:02:25.959 --> 00:02:29.949
right now, that what I saw about the

00:02:29.959 --> 00:02:32.430
economy crash is trying to manifest

00:02:32.440 --> 00:02:35.030
right in front of our faces, but the Lord

00:02:35.040 --> 00:02:37.070
is saying if we would

00:02:37.080 --> 00:02:40.470
pray and seek His face, He would give us

00:02:40.480 --> 00:02:42.990
this window of opportunity for the

00:02:43.000 --> 00:02:44.630
wealth of the wicked to be laid up for the

00:02:44.640 --> 00:02:48.430
righteous. We need this for

00:02:48.440 --> 00:02:51.710
the harvest; we need this wealth transfer.

00:02:51.720 --> 00:02:54.750
Listening to Him on a day-to-day basis,

00:02:54.760 --> 00:02:56.790
listening to Him on what to do with your

00:02:56.800 --> 00:03:00.110
finances, because God is going to be a

00:03:00.120 --> 00:03:02.070
rewarder of those that diligently seek

00:03:02.080 --> 00:03:04.589
Him. I don't believe it's for us to go

00:03:04.599 --> 00:03:07.390
into this crash of what I've seen coming

00:03:07.400 --> 00:03:11.390
with nothing and be there going, 'How

00:03:11.400 --> 00:03:14.030
are we going to do this?'I believe it's

00:03:14.040 --> 00:03:17.309
going to be a surplus on the body of

00:03:17.319 --> 00:03:20.789
Christ. For what I have seen, I told you, a

00:03:20.799 --> 00:03:23.390
remnant will walk in the

00:03:23.400 --> 00:03:25.990
blessing. I saw a one percent margin, and they go,

00:03:26.000 --> 00:03:28.990
'Well, you know, that's not enough.'Well,

00:03:28.990 --> 00:03:29.000
one percent

00:03:29.000 --> 00:03:31.789
out of a billion is pretty good. I

00:03:31.799 --> 00:03:33.270
mean, I don't know, that's

00:03:33.280 --> 00:03:34.869
a lot of folks. I don't know the math on

00:03:34.879 --> 00:03:36.509
it exactly, but I'm just

00:03:36.519 --> 00:03:39.229
saying that's a lot.

00:03:39.239 --> 00:03:41.589
So I'm not going to say the sky

00:03:41.589 --> 00:03:41.599
is

00:03:41.599 --> 00:03:44.270
falling, but I've told you all, I

00:03:44.280 --> 00:03:48.190
have seen a major economic shaking that

00:03:48.200 --> 00:03:51.949
is worse than the 1920s or 1930s, worse

00:03:51.959 --> 00:03:53.309
than the Great Depression. It was the

00:03:53.319 --> 00:03:55.110
Great Depression on

00:03:55.120 --> 00:03:56.990
steroids. I'm

00:03:57.000 --> 00:04:00.229
talking very bad

00:04:00.239 --> 00:04:02.710
looting, rioting, and pillaging like

00:04:02.720 --> 00:04:05.110
we've never seen before. People act crazy

00:04:05.120 --> 00:04:07.589
because it's not like it was in the

00:04:07.589 --> 00:04:07.599
thirties;

00:04:07.599 --> 00:04:10.550
people have no morals like they did

00:04:10.550 --> 00:04:10.560
then,

00:04:10.560 --> 00:04:13.550
some common

00:04:13.560 --> 00:04:18.430
sense. I saw places of refuge again. The Lord

00:04:18.440 --> 00:04:21.030
spoke about places

00:04:21.040 --> 00:04:24.070
having water. I saw

00:04:24.070 --> 00:04:24.080
a

00:04:24.080 --> 00:04:26.950
great drought again. I saw great

00:04:26.960 --> 00:04:29.189
manipulation with the weather again, and

00:04:29.199 --> 00:04:30.510
I thought it was very interesting

00:04:30.520 --> 00:04:32.270
because I was watching Benny

00:04:32.280 --> 00:04:35.029
Johnson's video about the JFK

00:04:35.039 --> 00:04:37.990
files. My son, my wife, and

00:04:37.990 --> 00:04:38.000
I

00:04:38.000 --> 00:04:39.870
were all watching it, and we were

00:04:39.880 --> 00:04:43.189
like, 'Oh dear God,'at how corrupt the CIA

00:04:43.199 --> 00:04:47.070
was back in

00:04:47.070 --> 00:04:47.080
the sixties.

00:04:47.080 --> 00:04:49.790
It was overwhelming,

00:04:49.800 --> 00:04:52.110
really, some of the things that were being

00:04:52.120 --> 00:04:53.749
said and what he was reading in the

00:04:53.759 --> 00:04:55.870
transcripts from those

00:04:55.870 --> 00:04:55.880
80,000-page

00:04:55.880 --> 00:04:57.710
reports

00:04:57.720 --> 00:05:00.670
about Israel, the nuclear

00:05:00.680 --> 00:05:04.510
capabilities, and

00:05:04.520 --> 00:05:07.670
setting up governments with

00:05:07.680 --> 00:05:10.830
all kinds of dirtiness. It was bad

00:05:10.840 --> 00:05:12.990
stuff; I was embarrassed

00:05:13.000 --> 00:05:14.870
as a citizen of the United States of

00:05:14.880 --> 00:05:16.710
America to hear that coming from our

00:05:16.720 --> 00:05:19.110
government, how corrupt

00:05:19.120 --> 00:05:22.270
they were even in the sixties. I was like, 'Wow, my

00:05:22.280 --> 00:05:25.110
dad was a little boy; this is

00:05:25.120 --> 00:05:28.430
really

00:05:28.430 --> 00:05:28.440
bad.'I'm

00:05:28.440 --> 00:05:30.749
just saying folks, it's

00:05:30.749 --> 00:05:30.759
eye-opening.

00:05:30.759 --> 00:05:33.590
And weather

00:05:33.600 --> 00:05:35.870
manipulation—they

00:05:35.880 --> 00:05:37.510
were using weather trying to figure out

00:05:37.520 --> 00:05:39.430
how to use weather manipulation to

00:05:39.430 --> 00:05:39.440
dethrone

00:05:39.440 --> 00:05:41.990
governments.

00:05:42.000 --> 00:05:43.390
This is what I've been

00:05:43.400 --> 00:05:45.670
praying over. I've told you all that

00:05:45.680 --> 00:05:48.029
they're going to use weather

00:05:48.039 --> 00:05:50.230
manipulation like we've never seen it

00:05:50.240 --> 00:05:53.230
before, and there will be drought in some

00:05:53.240 --> 00:05:56.550
areas and rain in another. It's

00:05:56.560 --> 00:05:59.670
going to be very serious drought and

00:05:59.680 --> 00:06:01.189
very serious

00:06:01.199 --> 00:06:03.270
floods.

00:06:03.280 --> 00:06:06.830
All that to say, I'm not

00:06:06.840 --> 00:06:10.150
afraid of it. I have total peace.

00:06:10.160 --> 00:06:11.950
Whenever people say, 'Are you tormented

00:06:11.960 --> 00:06:14.270
when you see these things?'No, I have

00:06:14.280 --> 00:06:17.390
total peace. I don't even let it get

00:06:17.390 --> 00:06:17.400
to

00:06:17.400 --> 00:06:19.749
me. I just go,

00:06:19.759 --> 00:06:27.189
'This isn't about me; this is about a shaking.'If

00:06:27.189 --> 00:06:27.199
I

00:06:27.199 --> 00:06:30.749
let my flesh

00:06:30.759 --> 00:06:33.870
look at it in the

00:06:33.880 --> 00:06:35.830
natural, yeah, you

00:06:35.840 --> 00:06:38.270
could get freaked out, but I stay

00:06:38.280 --> 00:06:40.350
spiritual about it and I stay in the

00:06:40.360 --> 00:06:42.749
spirit, praying in tongues over it. When

00:06:42.759 --> 00:06:45.070
the Lord shows me the things to come and

00:06:45.070 --> 00:06:45.080
warns

00:06:45.080 --> 00:06:46.950
you about these things, it's not for

00:06:46.960 --> 00:06:50.070
me to sound the alarm in fear

00:06:50.070 --> 00:06:50.080
like

00:06:50.080 --> 00:06:51.710
'Chicken Little, the sky is

00:06:51.710 --> 00:06:51.720
falling.'There's

00:06:51.720 --> 00:06:53.270
going to be a great economic

00:06:53.280 --> 00:06:55.110
crisis

00:06:55.110 --> 00:06:55.120
and

00:06:55.120 --> 00:06:57.390
people are

00:06:57.400 --> 00:06:59.670
going to stand in food lines for miles

00:06:59.680 --> 00:07:02.110
long.

00:07:02.120 --> 00:07:06.189
I'm saying it as a watchman

00:07:06.199 --> 00:07:09.270
seeing it, and I

00:07:09.280 --> 00:07:13.230
refuse to fear it because I have peace.

00:07:13.240 --> 00:07:14.830
You know when it's the Spirit of the

00:07:14.840 --> 00:07:16.790
Lord warning you about something versus

00:07:16.800 --> 00:07:18.270
the devil coming and tormenting you,

00:07:18.280 --> 00:07:20.230
it's

00:07:20.240 --> 00:07:22.589
when you have the peace

00:07:22.599 --> 00:07:24.550
that passes understanding

00:07:24.550 --> 00:07:24.560
while

00:07:24.560 --> 00:07:26.350
looking into something that should

00:07:26.360 --> 00:07:27.270
scare

00:07:27.280 --> 00:07:30.150
you, something that should make you

00:07:30.160 --> 00:07:32.710
crawl in a fetal

00:07:32.720 --> 00:07:33.790
position and

00:07:33.800 --> 00:07:36.629
rock. Does that freak me out right

00:07:36.639 --> 00:07:38.909
now when I'm telling you this? No. Why?

00:07:38.919 --> 00:07:40.670
Because I'm hearing the Spirit of the

00:07:40.680 --> 00:07:43.990
Lord warn me about something that's

00:07:44.000 --> 00:07:47.029
coming. When I see the plague and I see

00:07:47.039 --> 00:07:49.029
the people all on the cots, and

00:07:49.039 --> 00:07:50.670
I've seen all these things, was I in fear

00:07:50.680 --> 00:07:54.029
over that? No, not even a little bit,

00:07:54.039 --> 00:07:56.189
because I'm seeing it by the

00:07:56.199 --> 00:07:58.589
prophetic eye, the watchman eye.

00:07:58.599 --> 00:08:00.869
What the Lord's warned me about the plagues

00:08:00.879 --> 00:08:02.950
coming, I say none of that comes

00:08:02.950 --> 00:08:02.960
near

00:08:02.960 --> 00:08:06.149
me because He said if you stand on Psalm 91

00:08:06.159 --> 00:08:08.550
and

00:08:08.550 --> 00:08:08.560
Psalm

00:08:08.560 --> 00:08:11.830
23 and you get that down as a pillar in

00:08:11.840 --> 00:08:15.589
your heart, that no weapon formed against

00:08:15.599 --> 00:08:18.270
you will prosper. That's where we

00:08:18.280 --> 00:08:20.309
stay. We walk through the

00:08:20.319 --> 00:08:21.869
valley of the shadow of death, but we

00:08:21.879 --> 00:08:24.149
will fear no evil regardless of the

00:08:24.159 --> 00:08:25.950
plague, regardless of the pestilence. And

00:08:25.960 --> 00:08:28.790
the Lord showed me, He said, 'Brandon,

00:08:28.800 --> 00:08:30.029
America

00:08:30.039 --> 00:08:33.230
will be

00:08:33.230 --> 00:08:33.240
humbled.'That's

00:08:33.240 --> 00:08:35.829
not a word I want to tell

00:08:35.839 --> 00:08:37.949
everybody,

00:08:37.959 --> 00:08:41.790
but He said the church, the people,

00:08:41.800 --> 00:08:45.990
have a stiff neck towards Me, and in this,

00:08:46.000 --> 00:08:49.670
there will be a shaking to awaken

00:08:49.680 --> 00:08:52.990
again. I was looking at the hearts upon the

00:08:53.000 --> 00:08:57.590
land, and all of a sudden, all the hearts

00:08:57.600 --> 00:09:00.470
became one heart.

00:09:00.480 --> 00:09:03.269
It was very strange, but I

00:09:03.279 --> 00:09:04.910
could see all the hearts of the church

00:09:04.910 --> 00:09:04.920
and

00:09:04.920 --> 00:09:07.030
the nation, and all of

00:09:07.040 --> 00:09:09.470
them became one heart. The heart was

00:09:09.480 --> 00:09:10.910
black-looking

00:09:10.920 --> 00:09:13.949
and it had blood

00:09:13.959 --> 00:09:17.190
flowing from it.

00:09:17.200 --> 00:09:19.750
The center

00:09:19.760 --> 00:09:22.630
was starting to turn black.

00:09:22.640 --> 00:09:25.230
There was a little red left,

00:09:25.240 --> 00:09:27.190
but it was trying to

00:09:27.200 --> 00:09:29.590
turn into a black heart.

00:09:29.600 --> 00:09:31.630
What does that mean? I don't know. I see

00:09:31.640 --> 00:09:35.030
it and I pray over it, but it is alarming

00:09:35.040 --> 00:09:38.550
to me. It wasn't

00:09:38.560 --> 00:09:41.710
just one heart, one person; it was a vast

00:09:41.720 --> 00:09:45.949
majority of hearts, and it all became one

00:09:45.959 --> 00:09:48.310
heart. There was a little sliver of

00:09:48.320 --> 00:09:51.269
red in the middle, and all around

00:09:51.279 --> 00:09:53.710
it looked like it was toxic.

00:09:53.720 --> 00:09:57.269
The further it went out, it

00:09:57.279 --> 00:09:59.870
was black, and

00:09:59.870 --> 00:09:59.880
then

00:09:59.880 --> 00:10:02.069
it went into gray

00:10:02.079 --> 00:10:03.790
and then red.

00:10:05.519 --> 00:10:08.630
That's what I saw in the spirit. I

00:10:08.640 --> 00:10:09.949
haven't said that to anybody; even my

00:10:09.959 --> 00:10:12.310
family didn't know that. Some things I

00:10:12.320 --> 00:10:14.110
pray and I go, 'Oh, I probably should

00:10:14.120 --> 00:10:16.509
say that,'but that's what I

00:10:16.519 --> 00:10:19.990
saw.

00:10:22.720 --> 00:10:24.190
Then I saw the people with their

00:10:24.190 --> 00:10:24.200
noses

00:10:24.200 --> 00:10:26.150
stuck up and their

00:10:26.150 --> 00:10:26.160
necks

00:10:26.160 --> 00:10:28.069
were

00:10:28.079 --> 00:10:29.389
stiff. That's why I call them stiff-necked,

00:10:29.389 --> 00:10:29.399
because

00:10:29.399 --> 00:10:31.509
their necks were

00:10:31.519 --> 00:10:33.470
stiff. They

00:10:33.480 --> 00:10:35.949
were all upon the land and He said,

00:10:35.959 --> 00:10:38.949
'A great humbling is

00:10:38.949 --> 00:10:38.959
coming,'but

00:10:38.959 --> 00:10:41.310
I'm giving you a

00:10:41.320 --> 00:10:44.509
window for My beloved, for My

00:10:44.519 --> 00:10:47.430
remnant, so that this will not affect

00:10:47.440 --> 00:10:50.550
you if you're listening to Me. If

00:10:50.560 --> 00:10:54.230
you remember, Abraham

00:10:54.240 --> 00:10:58.590
interceded on behalf of Lot. Lot did not

00:10:58.600 --> 00:11:02.389
know that judgment was coming

00:11:02.399 --> 00:11:04.550
because

00:11:04.560 --> 00:11:06.470
he was

00:11:06.480 --> 00:11:09.030
living there and he was amongst them.

00:11:09.040 --> 00:11:12.030
Because he had

00:11:12.040 --> 00:11:13.110
become

00:11:13.120 --> 00:11:16.550
lukewarm and become part of Sodom

00:11:16.560 --> 00:11:19.269
and Gomorrah in the way they thought, he

00:11:19.279 --> 00:11:22.110
did not know that in a 24-hour period

00:11:22.120 --> 00:11:26.150
judgment was coming. So God sent an angelic

00:11:26.160 --> 00:11:29.269
host to go and get Lot and his family

00:11:29.279 --> 00:11:32.389
out of that

00:11:32.389 --> 00:11:32.399
hellhole,

00:11:32.399 --> 00:11:35.790
and he grabbed a hold of them

00:11:35.790 --> 00:11:35.800
because

00:11:35.800 --> 00:11:37.750
of intercessory

00:11:37.760 --> 00:11:43.550
prayer. Abraham interceded on behalf of

00:11:43.560 --> 00:11:46.949
Lot. My point

00:11:46.959 --> 00:11:49.550
is that many are

00:11:49.560 --> 00:11:53.310
Lots; many are in the cities and they

00:11:53.320 --> 00:11:54.990
don't know it because they've become so

00:11:55.000 --> 00:11:57.150
complacent and lukewarm that they're

00:11:57.160 --> 00:11:58.389
in the midst of it, and it's going to

00:11:58.399 --> 00:12:00.430
take an intercessor to pull you out by

00:12:00.440 --> 00:12:03.829
